column2: DELETE FROM IBANX_SIGNATURE WHERE OBJECT_ID IN (SELECT ID FROM IBANX_CHANGE_REQUEST WHERE NR = 'MOC-T00000002')
DELETE FROM IBANX_CHANGEREQUEST_LINK WHERE RA_OBJECT_ID NOT IN (SELECT ID FROM IBANX_CHANGE_REQUEST)
DELETE FROM IBANX_AUDIT_EVENT WHERE OBJECT_CLASS = 'ibanx.moc.ChangeRequest' AND OBJECT_ID NOT IN (SELECT ID FROM IBANX_CHANGE_REQUEST)
DELETE FROM IBANX_AUDIT_EVENT WHERE OBJECT_CLASS = 'ibanx.moc.ChangeAnalysis' AND OBJECT_ID NOT IN (SELECT ID FROM IBANX_CHANGEREQUEST_LINK WHERE LINKTYPE_NAME = 'request-analysis')
DELETE FROM IBANX_AUDIT_EVENT WHERE OBJECT_CLASS = 'ibanx.moc.ChangeActivity' AND OBJECT_ID NOT IN (SELECT ID FROM IBANX_CHANGEREQUEST_LINK WHERE LINKTYPE_NAME = 'request-activity')
DELETE FROM IBANX_CHANGE_ACTIVITY WHERE IS_TEMPLATE = 0 AND ID NOT IN (SELECT RB_OBJECT_ID FROM IBANX_CHANGEREQUEST_LINK WHERE LINKTYPE_NAME = 'request-activity')
DELETE FROM IBANX_CHANGE_ANALYSIS WHERE IS_TEMPLATE = 0 AND ID NOT IN (SELECT RB_OBJECT_ID FROM IBANX_CHANGEREQUEST_LINK WHERE LINKTYPE_NAME = 'request-analysis')
